          <physDesc>
            <objectDesc form="codex">
              <supportDesc material="chart">
                <support><material>paper</material></support>
                <extent> 
                  <measure type="composition" unit="leaf" quantity="263">263 ff.</measure> 
                  <dimensions type="leaf" unit="in">
                  <height><measure type="height" quantity="10.5" unit="in">10 1/2</measure></height>
                  <width><measure type="width" quantity="6.75" unit="in">6 3/4</measure></width>
                </dimensions>
                </extent>
                <foliation type="ancient">
                  <list>
                    <item target="#b1">
                      <locus from="1a" to="42"/>
                      <p>Genesis, marginally divided into 35 sections (<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܠܗ</foreign>).</p>
                    </item>
                    <item target="#b2">
                      <locus from="42b" to="101"/>
                      <p>Exodus, divided into 26 sections (<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܟܘ</foreign>).</p>
                    </item>
                  <item target="#b3">
                    <locus from="101a" to="147"/>
                    <p>Leviticus, divided into 20 sections (<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܟܟ</foreign>).</p>
                  </item>
                  <item target="#b4">
                    <locus from="147a" to="212"/>
                    <p>Numbers, divided into 26 sections (<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܟܘ</foreign>).</p>
                  </item>
                  <item>
                    <p>A few lessons (<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܩܪ̈ܝܢܐ</foreign>) have been marked on the margins; e.g. <locus from="40b" to="40b">foll. 40b</locus>, <locus from="41b" to="41b">41b</locus>, and <locus from="44b" to="44b">44b</locus>.</p>
                  </item>
                 </list>
                </foliation>
                <collation>
                  <p>The quires, signed with letters, were originally 30 in number</p>
                </collation>
                <condition>
                  <list>
                    <item>
                      <p>Some leaves are much torn, especially <locus from="1" to="1">foll. 1</locus>, <locus from="2" to="2">2</locus>, <locus from="8" to="8">8</locus>, <locus from="10" to="10">10</locus>, <locus from="23" to="23">23</locus>, <locus from="24" to="24">24</locus>, <locus from="26" to="26">26</locus>, <locus from="115" to="115">115</locus>, <locus from="262" to="262">262</locus>, and <locus from="263" to="263">263</locus>.</p>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                      <p>The missing portions of <ref target="#b1">Genesis</ref> are: ch. 1:1—4:12, 5:11—17:10, 18:5—27, 23:8—24:11, 31:53—36:4, and 36:30—37:15.</p>
                      <p>The missing portions of <ref target="#b5">Deuteronomy</ref> are: ch. 3:1—20, and 32:14— 34:12.</p>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                      <p>Of the 30 quires, the first (with the exception of a single leaf), the second, and the last, are now missing.</p>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                      <p>Leaves are also wanting after <locus from="2" to="2">foll. 2</locus>, <locus from="8" to="8">8</locus>, <locus from="22" to="22">22</locus>, <locus from="23" to="23">23</locus>, and <locus from="260" to="260">260</locus>.</p>
                    </item>
                  </list>
                </condition>
              </supportDesc>
              <layoutDesc>
                <layout columns="1" writtenLines="21 27">
                  <p>There are from 21 to 27 lines on each page.</p>
                </layout>
              </layoutDesc>
